    <item>
      <title>CFPB同意在机构退缩时撤销针对个人资金的案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-22/cfpb-agrees-to-drop-case-against-solo-funds-as-agency-cuts-back</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据法院申请，消费者金融保护局和点对点贷款平台独奏基金同意结束该机构针对该公司的诉讼，因为该公司对执法行动有更广泛的停顿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-22/cfpb-agrees-to-drop-case-against-solo-funds-as-agency-cuts-back</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Feb 2025 00:05:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
